## Microsoft Graph API Permissions

The following client `application` permissions are needed in order to use this {{.Type | lower}}:

**Required:**
- `Policy.ReadWrite.CrossTenantAccess`

**Optional (for read operations):**
- `Policy.Read.All`

Find out more about the permissions required for managing cross-tenant access policies at Microsoft Learn [here](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/crosstenantidentitysyncpolicypartner?view=graph-rest-beta).

